'''Borwa ba Afrika''' ke selete sa [[Afrika|Afrika]] seo se lego borwa ba naga. [[Thutafase|Thutafase]] le dipolotiki tša dinaga di a fapana ka dinaga tšeo dilego seleteng se.

== Thlalošišo ya Serepa ==
Goya ka ya [[Dilete tša UN|Delete tša UN]], dinaga tše tlhano tšeo diwelago seleteng sa Borwa ba Afrika ke:

* [[Afrika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]]
* [[Botswana|Botswana]]
* [[Lesotho|Lesotho]]
* [[Namibia|Namibia]]
* [[Swaziland|Swaziland]]

Dihlalošo tše dingwe di re dinaga tše dilatelago diwela seleteng se:
* [[Angola|Angola]]{{–}} e wela gape seleteng sa [[Bogare ba Afrika|Bogare ba Afrika]]
* [[Mozambique|Mozambique]] le [[Madagascar|Madagascar]]{{–}} e wela gape seleteng sa [[Afrika Bohlabela|Afrika Bohlabela]]
* [[Malawi|Malawi]], [[Zambia|Zambia]] le [[Zimbabwe|Zimbabwe]]{{–}} e wela gape seleteng sa [[Afrika Bohlabela|Afrika Bohlabela]]
* [[Comoros|Comoros]], [[Mauritius|Mauritius]], [[Seychelles|Seychelles]], [[Mayotte|Moyotte]] le [[Réunion|Réunion]]{{–}} dihlakehlake tšeo dilego [[Indian Ocean|Indian Ocean]]

Goya ka SADC (Appropos), [[Democratic Republic of the Congo|Democratic Republic of the Congo]] (e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare ba Afrika|Bogare ba Afrika]]) le [[Tanzania|Tanzania]] e wela seleteng sa [[Afrika Bohlabela|Afrika Bohlabela]]), di wela seleng sa Borwa ba Afrika. ''Apropos'', [[Southern African Development Community|Southern African Development Community]] (SADC) e hlomilew ka 1980 go hlohloletša tšhomišano magareng ga dinaga (tše lesome tee tlhano) seleteng.

